# Generated artifacts (spec 003 — interviews section)
# The /interviews/ tree is populated at build time and deployed via Pages.
# Source content lives under content/interviews/ (committed); HTML/JSON output
# lives under interviews/ (gitignored). Images are copied into interviews/images/
# from content/interviews/images/ during the build.
interviews/*.html
interviews/index.json
interviews/sitemap.xml
interviews/images/
!interviews/.gitkeep
